    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hi‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、まだいたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ you’re still here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……ごめん\n歌声が聞こえてきたものだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. Uh‚ sorry.\nI just heard you guys singing‚ so I came down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "今の、さくらちゃん達が\n次のステージで歌うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That song… are you girls going to\nsing it at your next performance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、まだ分からないけど……\nただ、こうやって声を合わせるの、いいなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we don’t know yet for sure‚\nbut it just feels so good singing together like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、私がメインボーカルになることが\n多かったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s because up until now\nI was usually the main vocals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今度はみんなで一緒に\n歌ってみないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why‚ for the next performance‚\nshe wanted us all to sing together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……ちゃんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… said so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私は反対だったんだけど……でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was against it… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしかして、良かった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! Are you glad you agreed to it now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。思ったよりは特徴が出てたかもしれない\n私達の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I think it has a lot more character than I expected it would.\nIt’s very “us.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だよね。私達の個性っていうか\nお日様みたいな暖かい感じ、あったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ right? It lets our unique personalities shine.\nShine warm like the sun! Did you hear it‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "…………みんなで歌うか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sing all together‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん達っぽいかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it really suits your group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "…………ヤバ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh-oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おい、麻……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ Mana!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（言いかけた俺は、慌てて口をつぐむと、さくら達に）\n（挨拶をしてその場を離れた。麻奈もその後に続く）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But I clamp a hand over my mouth‚ turn to Sakura and the others‚)\n(say goodbye‚ and leave. Mana follows me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 76.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 76.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 76.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "…………うう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughhh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまで元気だったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you were so full of life just a minute ago!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 83.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "……はは……だよね\nなんでだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… I know‚ right?\nWonder what happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "うう……\nうううう……重……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughhh…\nOh‚ oh… I feel heavy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 94.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "分かんないよ……\n幽霊なんて、初めてなったんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.\nI’ve never… been a ghost before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……なんか、凄く辛そうだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do? She looks like she’s in a lot of pain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 106.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（耳をすますと、さくらたちの歌声が聞こえてくる）\n（その歌が流れるにつれ、麻奈の体は少しずつ沈んでいく）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I strain my ears‚ and I can hear Sakura and her group singing.)\n(And the more they sing‚ the more Mana sinks into the floor.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 115.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "……しない……よね\nしちゃ……ダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won’t do it… right?\nI won’t let you… do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 121.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "何をしちゃダメなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What won’t you let us do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_04-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんの……歌を……止めちゃ……ダメ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t let you… stop Sakura… from singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 131.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
